This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with the problem of Machine Translation of Noisy Text (MTNT) dataset. It also involves the use of natural language processing techniques to enhance the robustness of MT systems. 

It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of machine learning techniques to improve the accuracy of MT systems. 

Additionally, it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of AI techniques to improve the performance of MT systems. 

It could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks to improve the accuracy of MT systems. 

Finally, it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves the use of pattern recognition techniques to identify and mitigate noise in MT systems.
